  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Every owner asks the same question the week before payday.",
      "checksum": "sha256:96b013689a3f324ab8cc12adf2d3967a4d5be52353249dd0715770a82dc5f25f",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Will I make it? You open five tabs. QuickBooks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:aca8a463fa5575367ab827444d2ba97be19c3520299ee5f8dff4ae85c03e5296",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "PayPal. Gmail. The bank. The payroll provider.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eea8b0bde3fe965d49240a6e9c64e9380ac6ffd6c80379a69899f00a4151fc0d",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 19
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "And by Sunday night you're still guessing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3625882a23e6f72f2f87fddd8eee8ef7fb3951cde65c54e6cebff3a488816d6c",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.043356009070295,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 26
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "But Anthropic just shipped something that answers it in five minutes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:75ee5015baa30a130c843c6fb23f521624ad09a6fbfb4549632b21fd287d1abf",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 33
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "And it's not a new model. It's a bundle.",
      "checksum": "sha256:62c1475c65afa088f47e532a52820a1dd0e957bfeded7b1bf63d5cdf3f5a0961",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "15 ready-to-run workflows, plus 15 reusable skills, pre-built and wired into the tools you already pay for.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d580e529c472a5a7bb165455c85c0b798b5071c70b629cad542bc4a7373f2683",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 6.594467120181406,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 53
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Invoice chaser. Margin analyzer. Month-end prepper.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bf48bfde87005dccb46b51abf2c461dbe4cd4aa8c6b8e7805930d974e1a1c975",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 70
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Tax-season organizer. Contract reviewer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dd05e7360bde3074e738d007dd86cadca8f41fda7eb4080a71490266920bc7dd",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 76
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Lead triager. The bundle is what's new, because the model was never the bottleneck.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6907071e809ca9af78ffcfc81ece5685c6dba67939c350632ddb23d7e51e3d9d",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 80
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "And these workflows don't sit in a chat window you bolt on.",
      "checksum": "sha256:10ad24e5d9720745298fb964023524259b0de6237ddcbef67979c52e1367d48f",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 94
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "They live inside QuickBooks, PayPal, HubSpot, Canva, DocuSign, Google Workspace, and Microsoft 365.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f662041cc177262e0f1a7aa15bd8cc4df271f9c1bcefb6ead94a1f60fccbb160",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 6.640907029478458,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "HubSpot calls it the first C R M connector for Claude.",
      "checksum": "sha256:488cc3271104eef18204d9d328c7d84690a9c2a4622f047547f26424c9be5a71",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 119
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "If you've ever tried to run an S M B with a generic chatbot that can't see your books, this is the difference.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6833ed161ca68bb0bc85ced4e70e83caa9d9f8bd94cadaaf20e0b954ac5fcb62",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 5.944308390022676,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 130
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Here's what it actually looks like. Full demo's in the description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ca07e88adc711d321dff8fa5e8edcd66570087d1bb8605f01965e8ad4514bca7",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 153
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Because this isn't built for the Fortune 500.",
      "checksum": "sha256:55bc24341f2955e909194061187995a7afda2dc9b6029fe158e81c81eed2ecfb",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 164
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Lina Ochman runs S M B at Anthropic, and her line is the receipt.",
      "checksum": "sha256:634a6c9a9166eab1c8282479a86da781d3aedd0b2c5ae3a62f5c72bf4d096991",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 172
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Not for the 15-person H V A C company. Not for the 30-person landscaper.",
      "checksum": "sha256:01e3d68427c6c6faf1ac6d3a69d462e5b03fe1ecf4a5357f78e8059520c92bad",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 186
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Not for the 50-person real estate brokerage.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0579f50d3668db11a0ffa72b933bf07e8f824a51b8d46dd1f4fe5429e25e2408",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 200
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Until now. And this isn't a rumor. Anthropic announced it on May 13th.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6e0008921201eeddcbc18afe170ed2a1e2e31e169481696c6a5d8ad4856303f4",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 207
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "And Canva just confirmed the partnership on X.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7687735b9ebf34ba8ab15a3e04eb5d3decc3b928345ef63e9455c955205fdd81",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 220
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "The receipts hold up. The customers do too.",
      "checksum": "sha256:931c4564af5aab7382d3800941a3cf717d597d92bf17fbf90e853da32a2cb501",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 228
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Plus the trust beat. Purity Coffee says Claude surfaced problems they didn't know they had.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8700ad03a1c52e531cb34964e5d29c0d02eb46a12bd651579b70fdc6247ae4e7",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 236
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Simple Modern says constraints aren't constraints anymore.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cbffb15c96755da531f86bd05b2288decd10c21225a9749d48a33a832b31a80c",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 251
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "MidCentral Energy says tedious clerical work just became value-add.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fa3d1c94c7b0c0048475569a53e5fd992c8ae784d42e1488d55fb7708d62be6a",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 258
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Every workflow runs approval-required by default.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b64637caaecfdfb9bd7cd2e606aa62a287391cb0371d6754bcc9666b6b9ffec5",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 267
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "And Anthropic doesn't train on your data.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f81129e70fa4b51e6baa43618817a2e3ab4ec0bfdd7851f6f6910896b69d58fd",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 2.136235827664399,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 273
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Half of small business owners cite security as their top hesitation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dec8bc4dd9ef5c099281fcbc751c31f18636f758e6be2ccee97d02e70b8fd31c",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 280
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Daniela Amodei calls this closing the gap on nearly half the American economy.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1b6247b2dc5769a36d74d20ce0a7ab93b4e41f0bfc932967975081fe314a46a0",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 291
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "So here's the question. You're already paying for Copilot.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e4511c95a5a5c16c6c9fafeb49b208d516f1c18dc373f9664e4f5380e813beaf",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 304
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Sunday-night payroll just dropped to five minutes inside the tools you already use.",
      "checksum": "sha256:347b3c67459cdc3189363c37696af90021cded3b527e3593dc52a064f871aac6",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 313
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "Switching from Copilot, or sticking? Drop your pick in the comments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:408800b01482d048365fa7eecc6fa9d5dcbc1b9a85ff9ac054a5cf229b436702",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 326
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "Subscribe for more AI news. And if you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eb5999accf07fd63bf2c226be27273c559db461c320e2c2202fd3726849757ff",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 6.315827664399093,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 337
    }
  ]
}